# DG-TWFD Phase 1

Industrialized Phase 1 scaffold for **Defect-Guided Time-Warp Flow Distillation (DG-TWFD)**. This stage implements a configuration center, structured logging, deterministic utilities, and a dummy teacher-driven data pipeline that emits `(x_t, x_s, t, s)` pairs for later student training.

## Pipeline Overview
Phase 1 only covers data preparation around the teacher flow map `Phi_T(t->s, x_t)`. The future student `M_theta(t, s, x_t)` and time-warp `u = g_phi(t)` are referenced in code comments and docstrings for mathematical continuity.

```text
x0 ~ p_data/noise
  |
  v
DummyTeacherTrajectory
  | make_trajectory / forward_map = Phi_T(t->s, x_t)
  v
TrajectoryPairDataset
  | sample t > s
  v
batch: {x_t, x_s, t, s}
  |
  v
future phases: M_theta, semigroup defect, g_phi
```

